cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with image processing and machine learning techniques to remove staff lines from music score images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) for staff line removal suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves the use of music symbol context, which suggests that it may belong to cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
